flowchart LR
  shopper[Shopper]
  admin[Admin]

  web[Web App\nNext.js]
  api[Core API Gateway\nNestJS]
  worker[Async Worker\nNestJS + BullMQ]
  ai[AI Service\nFastAPI + LangGraph]

  pg[(PostgreSQL)]
  redis[(Redis / BullMQ)]
  chroma[(Chroma Vector Store)]

  stripe[Stripe\nCheckout + Webhooks]
  resend[Resend\nEmail Delivery]
  s3[S3\nProduct Media]
  gemini[Gemini APIs\nLLM + Embeddings]
  sentry[Sentry]
  langsmith[LangSmith]

  shopper -->|browse, cart, checkout, assistant chat| web
  admin -->|admin dashboard + product management| web
  web -->|REST + SSE| api

  api -->|proxy AI chat/stream| ai
  api -->|domain reads/writes| pg
  api -->|enqueue jobs| redis
  worker -->|consume jobs| redis
  worker -->|read order snapshot| pg
  worker -->|send order confirmation| resend

  api -->|create/retrieve checkout sessions| stripe
  stripe -->|payment webhooks| api
  api -->|presign + media metadata| s3

  ai -->|catalog retrieval| pg
  ai -->|semantic retrieval index| chroma
  ai -->|planner/synthesis/embeddings| gemini

  web -.->|frontend errors/traces| sentry
  api -.->|backend errors/traces| sentry
  ai -.->|service errors/traces| sentry
  ai -.->|graph traces| langsmith
